acsse.csc2a.entities

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • acsse.csc2a.entities.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDrawable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enermy, Ice, Player, Snake

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDrawable
    The abstract GameObject class is the base class that contains game objects(player, enemy and weapon) It also implements the IDrawable interface which allows the objects to be drawable on the Game Panel
